5000|$|In 2001, {{a special}} yellow SC2 coupé model was also built. The model was officially named [...] "Limited Edition", but soon {{became known as}} the [...] "Bumblebee Edition". 99 were produced, each with a <b>certificate</b> <b>of</b> <b>authenticity.</b> The [...] "Bumblebee Edition" [...] {{included}} embroidered headrests, black leather interior with yellow leather inserts on the seats and door panels, black roof and mirrors, number designation inside fuel filler door and <b>certificate</b> <b>of</b> <b>authenticity.</b> These are {{not to be confused with}} the regular issue Yellow Sport Coupe.|$|R
